{"tid":2099321,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【連續三天】美軍機再抵近中国沿岸偵察　距廣東海岸線不足百公里","createTime":"2020-07-08T06:49:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-08T06:54:03.000Z","uid":184679,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b917780b22d45e5be2d4e7f86cc63c380d097f91","tid":2099321,"uid":184679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T06:49:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200708/357535221320650752.jpeg/ZLWOLAIvrPrW_YJjAK1q43_PUV-L3iJbvjLfOr4y3zo?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200708%2F357535221320650752.jpeg%2FZLWOLAIvrPrW_YJjAK1q43_PUV-L3iJbvjLfOr4y3zo%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=0cd6918a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n美軍軍機EP-3E電子偵察機被發現周三（8日）再次抵近中國沿岸偵察，一度飛至距離廣東省海岸線約95.7公里。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200708/357533936542420992.jpeg/lOh-PpYF6GqmG0sSLNdrZW97PvDuLVoo3E4uC9xOLgs?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200708%2F357533936542420992.jpeg%2FlOh-PpYF6GqmG0sSLNdrZW97PvDuLVoo3E4uC9xOLgs%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=06fe0270&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美軍軍機一度抵近至距離廣東沿岸約51.68海里，即約95.7公里。（Twitter）<br />\n<br />\n綜合傳媒報道，美軍軍機飛經巴士海峽，由南往北靠近台海中線後，再折往西南飛行，同時抵近廣東沿岸進行偵察。報道更稱，美軍軍機的距離較周二（7日）的約111公里更近，只有約95.7公里。<br />\n<br />\n另據北京大學海洋研究院「南海戰略態勢感知計劃」在社交平台上發布的消息指出，美軍已是連續三天派出軍機抵近中國進行偵察。周一（6日）時是一架RC-135偵察機，周二時則是EP-3E電子偵察機。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200708/357534706411114496.jpeg/wSVXrr3DyZmZ8m7Y_LbsXPTpFLNpllMSZeoLtGXqC7Q?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200708%2F357534706411114496.jpeg%2FwSVXrr3DyZmZ8m7Y_LbsXPTpFLNpllMSZeoLtGXqC7Q%3Fv%3Dw640&h=82f0d342&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200708/357534704007778304.jpeg/UPKw8l-xIYC4plKxp76CjmWIzN11W4IE68uutevLrrU?v=w640\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200708%2F357534704007778304.jpeg%2FUPKw8l-xIYC4plKxp76CjmWIzN11W4IE68uutevLrrU%3Fv%3Dw640&h=579e14a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n值得一提是，中國國防部發言人吳謙大校在周一的例行記者會上，曾經對美軍的行為作出回應。吳謙稱，當前在地區國家的共同努力下，東海、南海的局勢總體是穩定，充分說明域內國家有智慧、有能力、有辦法通過直接談判協商，妥處分歧，共護和平。反觀作為域外國家的美國，打著所謂「航行自由」的幌子，派軍用艦機來東海、南海挑釁，對中國實施高頻度抵近偵察，舉行針對性極強的軍事演習，嚴重危害地區國家的主權與安全利益，嚴重破壞本地區的和平穩定。<br />\n<br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">https://www.hk01.com/即時中國/495411/</code></pre>"},{"pid":"671030dd53080a93cabebd1892fb6653c6685ee5","tid":2099321,"uid":135408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T06:52:36.000Z","msg":"嗯<br />\n口交部又出黎講兩句<br />\n解放軍飛機升空攔截警告進入我國領土乜乜乜<br />\n都係冇事會發生"},{"pid":"8be4ded14617de5cdb95be9d4dec0ce27df63ffa","tid":2099321,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T06:53:34.000Z","msg":"應該係睇到對台有動作"},{"pid":"9d62a4e3a412c15defa16aaed3d5f7ea3aa46610","tid":2099321,"uid":143343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-08T06:54:03.000Z","msg":"放心，China joe 一上台<br />\n<br />\n應該唔會再有"}]}